    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes a common methodology for the automated benchmarking of Virtualized Network Functions (VNFs) executed on general-purpose hardware. Specific cases of automated benchmarking methodologies for particular VNFs can be derived from this document. An open source reference implementation is reported as running code embodiment of the proposed, automated benchmarking methodology.</t>
